Taking Lizards' treasures
The treasures of the Lizards lie on the farthest of the three islands located in the southern part of the lake. Lizards do not like to part with their treasures, but it may prove worthwhile for you to try and capture them!
#subobj  1
Find the treasure
The three islands in the southern part of the lake are connected by bridges. You must go to the farthest island.
#subobj  2
Get the treasure
The treasures belonging to the Lizards are hidden in the coffer. Open it and take the treasure.
